caption.p: Phylogenetic tree for RSV-A, based on partial sequences of the G-protein gene. Protein sequence ranges from amino acid position 54 up to stop codon. +N and −N indicate gain and loss of N-glycosylation sites and +O and −O indicate gain and loss of O-glycosylation sites. Country codes in the virus names: ITA = Italy; JOR = Jordan; Kilifi = Kenya; MEX = Mexico; NZL = New Zealand; PER = Peru; US or USA = United States of America.
